seo_data.meta_title: How to Help a Sick Baby Sleep | AVEENO®
seo_data.meta_description: How to Help a Sick Baby Sleep When a baby has a cold, it can mean long, sleepless nights for everyone. And, often, this lack of sleep becomes part of a vicious cycle: baby gets sick and doesn’t sleep well and, as a result, doesn’t get the critical shut eye they need to kick their congestion, fever and general icks. Because of this, illnesses wear on longer than they should, and sleep continues to be a battle night after night -- and that means you’re getting less shut-eye, too.
